beer.beer_description:
This light-bodied fruited sour beer, is brewed in the style of a traditional German gose.

Its high mineral content balances out the acidity and makes for dry and refreshing finish.

Here, the ‘fruit salad’ is brought by the addition of mango, passionfruit and pineapple, resulting in a sessionable beer with an ultra-tropical twist!
